{"prompt": "Generate a website for a professional law firm. The website should be dynamic and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Apex Legal Group</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --primary-color: #8b0000; /* Dark Red */\n            --secondary-color: #d3d3d3; /* Light Gray */\n            --text-color: #333333;\n            --background-color: #f4f4f4;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: auto;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            padding: 0 20px;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background: var(--primary-color);\n            color: #ffffff;\n            padding-top: 30px;\n            min-height: 70px;\n            border-bottom: #8b0000 3px solid;\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            text-align: center;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding-bottom: 10px;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n        }\n\n        header nav {\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-top: 10px;\n            padding-bottom: 10px;\n        }\n\n        header nav a {\n            color: #ffffff;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            text-transform: uppercase;\n            font-size: 16px;\n            padding: 0 15px;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        header nav a:hover {\n            color: var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        #hero {\n            min-height: 400px;\n            background: url('https://via.placeholder.com/1500x400/8b0000/ffffff?text=Apex+Legal+Group') no-repeat center center/cover;\n            text-align: center;\n            color: #ffffff;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            position: relative;\n        }\n\n        #hero::before {\n            content: '';\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 0;\n            left: 0;\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); /* Dark overlay for better text readability */\n        }\n\n        #hero h2 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            font-size: 3em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.7);\n        }\n\n        #hero p {\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            text-shadow: 1px 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,0.7);\n        }\n\n        .button {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background: var(--primary-color);\n            color: #ffffff;\n            padding: 12px 30px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            font-size: 18px;\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.2s ease;\n            cursor: pointer;\n        }\n\n        .button:hover {\n            background: #a00000;\n            transform: translateY(-2px);\n        }\n\n        #services, #about, #contact {\n            padding: 40px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        #services h3, #about h3, #contact h3 {\n            font-size: 2em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n        }\n\n        .service-item, .contact-info {\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            padding: 20px;\n            background: #ffffff;\n            border-left: 5px solid var(--primary-color);\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n\n        .service-item h4 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n        }\n\n        #contact form {\n            max-width: 600px;\n            margin: 20px auto;\n            text-align: left;\n        }\n\n        #contact input[type=\"text\"],\n        #contact input[type=\"email\"],\n        #contact textarea {\n            width: 100%;\n            padding: 10px;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n            border: 1px solid var(--secondary-color);\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            box-sizing: border-box; /* Include padding and border in the element's total width and height */\n        }\n\n        #contact textarea {\n            height: 150px;\n            resize: vertical;\n        }\n\n        #contact button {\n            display: block;\n            width: 100%;\n            background: var(--primary-color);\n            color: #ffffff;\n            padding: 12px 0;\n            font-size: 18px;\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.2s ease;\n        }\n\n        #contact button:hover {\n            background: #a00000;\n            transform: translateY(-2px);\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background: var(--primary-color);\n            color: #ffffff;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n        }\n\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h1>Apex Legal Group</h1>\n            <nav>\n                <a href=\"#hero\">Home</a>\n                <a href=\"#services\">Services</a>\n                <a href=\"#about\">About Us</a>\n                <a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a>\n            </nav>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <section id=\"hero\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Your Trusted Legal Partners</h2>\n            <p>Providing expert legal counsel with integrity and dedication.</p>\n            <a href=\"#contact\" class=\"button\">Schedule a Consultation</a>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"services\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h3>Our Practice Areas</h3>\n            <div class=\"row\">\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <h4>Corporate Law</h4>\n                    <p>Navigating complex business transactions and regulatory compliance.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <h4>Litigation</h4>\n                    <p>Aggressive and strategic representation in all courts.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <h4>Real Estate Law</h4>\n                    <p>Assisting with property transactions, zoning, and development.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <h4>Intellectual Property</h4>\n                    <p>Protecting your innovations and brand identity.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"about\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h3>About Apex Legal Group</h3>\n            <p>Founded on the principles of excellence, ethics, and client advocacy, Apex Legal Group is a distinguished law firm committed to delivering unparalleled legal services. Our team of seasoned attorneys brings a wealth of experience across diverse legal domains, ensuring that your needs are met with precision and professionalism. We believe in building strong relationships with our clients, understanding their unique challenges, and forging effective solutions.</p>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"contact\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h3>Get In Touch</h3>\n            <div class=\"contact-info\">\n                <p><strong>Address:</strong> 123 Law Street, Legal City, LC 45678</p>\n                <p><strong>Phone:</strong> (123) 456-7890</p>\n                <p><strong>Email:</strong> info@apexlegal.com</p>\n            </div>\n            <form id=\"contactForm\">\n                <input type=\"text\" name=\"name\" placeholder=\"Your Name\" required>\n                <input type=\"email\" name=\"email\" placeholder=\"Your Email\" required>\n                <textarea name=\"message\" placeholder=\"Your Message\" required></textarea>\n                <button type=\"submit\">Send Message</button>\n            </form>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2023 Apex Legal Group. All rights reserved.</p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        document.getElementById('contactForm').addEventListener('submit', function(event) {\n            event.preventDefault();\n            alert('Thank you for your message! We will be in touch shortly.');\n            this.reset();\n        });\n    </script>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"}